217
00:15:17.614 --> 00:15:19.533
Marlon ada masalah.

218
00:15:31.420 --> 00:15:32.838
<i>Ia dipanggil Lonette.</i>

219
00:15:33.505 --> 00:15:36.341
<i>Dia baru sahaja ditinggalkan.</i>

