259
00:17:44.970 --> 00:17:46.805
Hei, orang tak dikenali.

260
00:17:48.515 --> 00:17:49.600
Hei.

261
00:17:56.648 --> 00:17:57.733
Carol.

262
00:17:58.442 --> 00:17:59.985
Hai, Carol.

263
00:18:00.068 --> 00:18:01.570
- Hai.
