283
00:19:38.500 --> 00:19:39.835
Bukan malam ini, Alfred.

284
00:19:40.252 --> 00:19:42.754
- Kenapa? Beritahu saya.
- Saya cuma...


285
00:19:43.005 --> 00:19:45.215
- Apa?
- Agaknya saya...


286
00:19:46.466 --> 00:19:48.760
Saya rasa marah.

287
00:20:04.860 --> 00:20:06.904
Kesiannya, dia hampir mati.

288
00:20:07.195 --> 00:20:09.865
Sudah lama awak menyeksa dia.

289
00:20:10.073 --> 00:20:11.909
Alfie, dia patut memikirkan semua itu

290
00:20:12.034 --> 00:20:15.037
