00:27:00.359 --> 00:27:01.735
Saya telah melamar dia.

381
00:27:07.449 --> 00:27:09.284
Awak tahu awak
pengapit lelaki saya, bukan?


382
00:27:11.203 --> 00:27:12.663
<i>Pengajaran cerita ini...</i>

